{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"body":"Decomposed the implementation into four scoped child stories with explicit acceptance-criterion ownership, file-impact metadata, DD-level proving commands, and dependency links. The completed worktree experiment remains parent-level evidence. Delivery graph: immune-floury-toad -> {truthful-specified-silverfish, indigoid-unmystic-serpent} -> taurine-catchable-kakarikis."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784164176178638001,"uuid":"e3675785-f7c6-40aa-804e-318fd1f63405"}